rules.ruleString: Must be enrolled in course type {04, 05, 06, 06G, 07, 07G, 07PG, 11, 42, 50PG, 76, 78}

description: Current community health concerns and the preoccupations of health policy and services. Frameworks for conceptualising and assessing the health concerns that impact on individuals, families and communities, are analysed and applied to specific health concerns.
faculty: Faculty of Medicine, Nursing and Health Sciences
